  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, biomarker response after supplementation with oral and intramuscular vitamin
      B12 will be compared in a randomized clinical trial. Electronic compliance monitoring will be
      used to control for non compliance as a possible confounder in oral treatment. Additionally
      subjective acceptance in terms of presumed preferences will be compared with oral vs.
      intramuscular supplementation of vitamin B12 in the view of the patient.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
